          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A14W2-line-1" n="1">T<hi rend="small-caps">HE</hi> furniture that best doth please</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A14W2-line-2" n="2">St Patrick's Dean, good Sir, are these:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A14W2-line-3" n="3">The knife and fork with which I eat;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A14W2-line-4" n="4">And next the pot that boils the meat;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A14W2-line-5" n="5">The next to be preferr'd, I think,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A14W2-line-6" n="6">Is the glass in which I drink;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A14W2-line-7" n="7">The shelves on which my books I keep,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A14W2-line-8" n="8">And the bed on which I sleep;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A14W2-line-9" n="9">An antique elbow-chair between,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A14W2-line-10" n="10">Big enough to hold the Dean;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A14W2-line-11" n="11">And the stove that gives delight</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A14W2-line-12" n="12">In the cold bleak wintry night:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A14W2-line-13" n="13">To these we add a thing below,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A14W2-line-14" n="14">More for use reserved than show:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A14W2-line-15" n="15">These are what the Dean do please;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A14W2-line-16" n="16">All superfluous are but these.</l>
          </lg>
